# ========================================================================================
# HOW TO GET CREDENTIALS
# ========================================================================================
# YouTube: https://console.cloud.google.com/ → Create project → Enable YouTube Data API v3
# TikTok: https://developers.tiktok.com/ → Register → Get credentials
# Instagram: https://developers.facebook.com/ → Create app → Link Instagram account
# Facebook: https://developers.facebook.com/ → Create app → Generate Page Access Token
# All others: Visit respective developer portals and create applications

# ========================================================================================
# DEPLOYMENT
# ========================================================================================
# Production (Cloudflare):
#   1. Go to Workers → Settings → Variables
#   2. Add all environment variables
#   3. Use "Encrypt" for sensitive values
#   Or use: npx wrangler secret put KEY_NAME
